                    An international consulting firm helping entrepreneurs worldwide establish and manage businesses in the US and UAE is looking for an experienced tax accountant to support foreign-owned LLC clients with compliance, filings, and advisory.



Responsibilities:

? Prepare and file US tax forms: Form 5472 + Pro Forma 1120, Form 1040-NR, Form 1065;

? Handle entity elections (Form 8832, Form 2553) and extensions (Form 7004);

? Ensure compliance with IRS requirements for foreign-owned LLCs;

? Monitor reporting obligations including BOI / FinCEN;

? Track deadlines and maintain accurate documentation;

? Advise clients on USTB, ECI, and non-resident tax exposure;

? Support clients in structuring operations and minimizing tax risks.



Requirements:

? 3+ years of experience with US LLC taxation;

? Strong experience with Form 5472 and foreign-owned disregarded entities;

? Solid understanding of IRS compliance and reporting requirements;

? Attention to detail and structured approach to work.



Working Conditions:

? Competitive salary (based on experience);

? Fully remote work format;

? Work with international clients (e-commerce, SaaS, consulting, digital services);

? Long-term cooperation with a growing global company.
